Field Detail

param

public ImmutableSvmParameterPoint<L extends Comparable,P> param
a thing that is confusing here: if a grid search was done, then the specific point that was the optimum should be recorded here. That works for binary and multiclass models when the grid search is done at the top level. But when param.gridsearchBinaryMachinesIndependently, there is no one point that makes sense. Really we should just leave it null and refer to the subsidiary BinaryModels.
